text: Round Pond is an reservoir in Duxbury, Massachusetts. The reservoir is located northeast of Pine Lake, northwest of Island Creek Pond, and southwest of North Hill Marsh Pond. An inlet provides the inflow for this reservoir from Pine Lake. The reservoir is associated hydro logically with an adjacent cranberry bog operation. ==External links== *Environmental Protection Agency *South Shore Coastal Watersheds - Lake Assessments Category:Lakes of Plymouth County, Massachusetts Category:Duxbury, Massachusetts Category:Reservoirs in Massachusetts
